  "texts": [
    "If so, that probably entails the existence of a soul, or psyche, or aura, that can either be an energy form that exists around us or resides in the realms of a colorful nebula; thousands of lightyears away in a galaxy hidden in the vast depth of the Universe, likely unknown to us.",
    "That entangled being can even exist in the present or (through an Einstein-Rosen bridge) far in the future, or even at the Big Bang.",
    "So, maybe our consciousness might be a creation of a collective version of our future selves, or an afterthought of a simulacra never created but emancipated.",
    "Could we prove its existence?",
    "Even if the suggested philosophical hypothesis reaches to the fringes of science and enters the realms of fiction, there is something even more questionable."
